---
import DocsLayout from "../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
import Callout from "../../components/docs/Callout.astro";
---

<DocsLayout title="Configuración - Documentación">
  <h1>Configuración Inicial</h1>

  <p class="lead">
    Personaliza el sistema para adaptarlo a la identidad y operativa de tu
    restaurante.
  </p>

  <h2 class="mb-6">Acceso Administrativo</h2>

  <p class="mb-8">
    Una vez instalado, el sistema genera credenciales por defecto para el primer
    acceso.
  </p>

  <!-- Login Mockup -->
  <div class="relative max-w-sm mx-auto my-12 not-prose group">
    <!-- Glow Effect -->
    <div
      class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl blur opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-1000 group-hover:duration-200"
    >
    </div>

    <div
      class="relative p-8 bg-[#0f172a] border border-white/10 rounded-xl shadow-2xl"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
        <div
          class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-lg shadow-primary-500/20"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="w-6 h-6 text-white"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            ><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"
            ></path><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"></polyline></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg">RestaurantePOS</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Iniciar Sesión</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div>
          <label
            class="block text-xs text-slate-400 mb-1.5 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider"
            >Email</label
          >
          <div
            class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 bg-[#1e293b] rounded-lg border border-white/5 text-slate-300"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-500"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              ><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"></rect><path
                d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"></path></svg
            >
            <span class="font-mono text-sm">admin@mirestaurante.com</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <label
            class="block text-xs text-slate-400 mb-1.5 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider"
            >Contraseña</label
          >
          <div
            class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 bg-[#1e293b] rounded-lg border border-white/5 text-slate-300"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-500"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              ><rect width="18" height="11" x="3" y="11" rx="2" ry="2"
              ></rect><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path></svg
            >
            <span class="font-mono text-sm">admin123</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button
          class="w-full py-3 bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-500 text-white rounded-lg font-bold text-sm transition-all shadow-lg shadow-primary-500/20 mt-4"
        >
          Ingresar al Dashboard
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Callout type="warning" title="Seguridad">
    Cambia estas credenciales inmediatamente después del primer inicio de sesión
    desde el perfil de usuario.
  </Callout>

  <h2 class="mb-4">Datos del Establecimiento</h2>

  <p class="mb-8">
    Navega a <code>Dashboard > Configuración</code> para editar la información que
    aparecerá en tus comprobantes.
  </p>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 not-prose mb-12">
    <!-- Item 1 -->
    <div
      class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#1e293b]/30"
    >
      <div class="p-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 mt-1">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="w-5 h-5"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          ><path
            d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z"
          ></path><path
            d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z"
          ></path></svg
        >
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-sm">Razón Social</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">
          Nombre legal que aparecerá en facturas.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Item 2 -->
    <div
      class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#1e293b]/30"
    >
      <div class="p-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 mt-1">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="w-5 h-5"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          ><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"></rect><line
            x1="12"
            x2="12"
            y1="11"
            y2="17"></line><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="7" y2="7.01"></line></svg
        >
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-sm">RUC</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">
          Registro Único de Contribuyentes para SUNAT.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Item 3 -->
    <div
      class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#1e293b]/30"
    >
      <div class="p-2 rounded-lg bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-400 mt-1">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="w-5 h-5"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          ><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"
          ></path><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle></svg
        >
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-sm">Dirección Fiscal</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">
          Ubicación registrada ante la entidad tributaria.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Item 4 -->
    <div
      class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#1e293b]/30"
    >
      <div class="p-2 rounded-lg bg-pink-500/10 text-pink-400 mt-1">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="w-5 h-5"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          ><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><circle
            cx="9"
            cy="9"
            r="2"></circle><path d="m21 15-3.086-3.086a2 2 0 0 0-2.828 0L6 21"
          ></path></svg
        >
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-sm">Logo Corporativo</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">
          Formato PNG/JPG para tickets y sistema.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>
    Series de Facturación <span
      class="bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full border border-blue-500/20 align-middle ml-2 font-mono"
      >SUNAT</span
    >
  </h2>

  <p>
    El sistema requiere configurar las series para la emisión de comprobantes
    electrónicos.
  </p>

  <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 not-prose my-8">
    <!-- Invoice Type F -->
    <div
      class="bg-[#1e293b] rounded-xl border border-white/5 overflow-hidden group hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all"
    >
      <div
        class="bg-blue-600/20 p-3 flex justify-center border-b border-white/5 group-hover:bg-blue-600/30 transition-colors"
      >
        <div
          class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500 text-white text-xs font-bold rounded shadow-lg uppercase tracking-wider"
        >
          Factura
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 text-center">
        <div
          class="text-3xl font-mono text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors"
        >
          F001
        </div>
        <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">
          Serie Default
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Invoice Type B -->
    <div
      class="bg-[#1e293b] rounded-xl border border-white/5 overflow-hidden group hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-all"
    >
      <div
        class="bg-emerald-600/20 p-3 flex justify-center border-b border-white/5 group-hover:bg-emerald-600/30 transition-colors"
      >
        <div
          class="px-3 py-1 bg-emerald-500 text-white text-xs font-bold rounded shadow-lg uppercase tracking-wider"
        >
          Boleta
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 text-center">
        <div
          class="text-3xl font-mono text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors"
        >
          B001
        </div>
        <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">
          Serie Default
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Invoice Type T -->
    <div
      class="bg-[#1e293b] rounded-xl border border-white/5 overflow-hidden group hover:border-amber-500/30 transition-all"
    >
      <div
        class="bg-amber-600/20 p-3 flex justify-center border-b border-white/5 group-hover:bg-amber-600/30 transition-colors"
      >
        <div
          class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber-500 text-white text-xs font-bold rounded shadow-lg uppercase tracking-wider"
        >
          Ticket
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 text-center">
        <div
          class="text-3xl font-mono text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors"
        >
          T001
        </div>
        <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">
          Uso Interno
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Callout type="note" title="Multi-serie">
    Si tienes múltiples cajas o sucursales, puedes crear nuevas series (e.g. <code
      >B002</code
    >, <code>F002</code>) desde el panel de administración.
  </Callout>
</DocsLayout>
